            </div> -->
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Hi there! I'm <%=name%>, a dedicated Computer Science
                student currently studying at <%=university%>. I'm deeply interested
                    in <%=interest%>.

                        Throughout my academic journey, I've been building my skills in <%=skills%>, and I've worked on
                            several projects that have helped me apply what I've
                            learned in the classroom to real-world scenarios. These projects include <%=projects%>.

                                I'm constantly seeking to learn more and improve my skills, whether it's by taking on
                                new projects,
                                participating in hackathons, or exploring the latest tech trends. My goal is to continue
                                growing as a
                                developer and eventually contribute to creating meaningful and impactful software.

                                Outside of my studies, I enjoy <%=hobbies%>. I'm always eager to connect with others,
                                    collaborate on projects, and learn from new
                                    experiences.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="projects" style=" padding: 60px 20px; text-align: center;">
        <h2>My Projects</h2>
        <div class="project-grid">
            <div class="project">
                <h3>CRUD PROJECT</h3>
                <p>It's a student management website for showing crud operation, create using Node.js,Html,Css,Js</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <h3>Personal Protfolio</h3>
                <p>It's a portfolio website, create using express.js,html,css</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>


    <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Contact Me</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or opportunities, feel free to reach out to me!</p>
            <form action="/contact" method="POST" class="contact-form">
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>

                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>

                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>

                <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>

